<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink331">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi yaviḻiṇark</l>
<l>karuṅkāṉ marāattu vaikuciṉai vāṉpū</l>
<l>varuñcurañ celluna roḻintō ruḷḷa</l>
<l>viṉiya kamaḻum veṟpi</l>
<l>ṉiṉṉā teṉpa vavarceṉṟa vāṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>They say that pleasing not is the path he followed, </l>
<l>because of the mountains where white flowers on the branches </l>
<l>growing from the black-stemmed Kadamba trees with opening clusters, </l>
<l>emit pleasant fragrance, making travellers across harsh desert  </l>
<l>think about those who are left behind. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
